---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Boxed Water — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Boxed Water made palletizing its first end-of-line automation with Formic — taking 28-pound lifts off its people and easing a summer reliance on temp labor, with no upfront capital."
  ogTitle="Boxed Water — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="96% plant-based · 1.5M+ trees planted · first robot, zero risk"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/boxed-water" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Boxed Water
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Boxed Water</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">How Boxed Water Is Taking the Strain Out of the Line with Automation</h1>
    <p class="lede">Boxed Water — cartons up to 96% plant-based, 1.5 million trees planted — made palletizing its first end-of-line automation, taking the 28-pound lifts off its people and easing a summer reliance on temp labor.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/boxed-water-hero.jpg" alt="Boxed Water carton line and palletizing" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Boxed Water · Holland, Michigan</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">2009</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Holland, Michigan</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Sustainable beverages</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Cartons</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Up to 96% plant-based</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Trees planted</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1.5 million+</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Heavy lifts, <em>long shifts</em>.</h2>
      <p>Boxed Water, founded in 2009 in Holland, Michigan, runs two shifts making cartons up to 96% plant-based — and has planted over 1.5 million trees across the U.S. Most of the filler line is already automated, but manual palletizing of 28-pound cases, even with ergonomic pallet tables, had become the bottleneck straining its people.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>28-pound cases stacked by hand</li>
        <li>Filler line automated — palletizing the bottleneck</li>
        <li>Two shifts of heavy manual labor</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/boxed-water-2.jpg" alt="Boxed Water cartons on the production line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Cartons · up to 96% plant-based</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic Full Service palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">First robot · low risk</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>First robot in, <em>risk out</em>.</h2>
      <p>This is Boxed Water's first end-of-line automation, and it chose Formic's Full Service model over buying — no upfront capital, with Formic owning system performance. It also eases a long-standing reliance on temporary labor during the summer spike, when higher temperatures and event partnerships drive demand and a constant onboarding burden.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>First end-of-line automation for the plant</li>
        <li>Full Service: no capital, Formic owns performance</li>
        <li>Less reliance on seasonal temp labor</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"With Formic, the cost to entry is low and the risk is low. I'm not expending all that capital up front to force myself to make it work; that's their job."</blockquote>
      <cite>Rick Kulas · Director of Operations, Boxed Water</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Lighter line. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Lighter footprint.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">96%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Plant-based cartons</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">1.5M+</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Trees planted</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">28 lb</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Cases now automated</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Take the strain <em>off your line</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
